<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>Payment Failed – Mission Bazar</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: #c0392b; color: #fff; padding: 24px 32px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 22px; }
    .body { padding: 28px 32px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 13px; }
    .info-row span:first-child { color: #777; }
    .cta { text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; }
    .cta a { background: #1a1a2e; color: #fff; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; }
    .footer { background: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; padding: 14px; font-size: 11px; color: #999; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="header"><h1>Payment Failed</h1></div>
  <div class="body">
    <p>Hi <strong><%= customerName %></strong>,</p>
    <p>Unfortunately your payment could not be processed.</p>
    <div class="info-row"><span>Transaction ID</span><span><%= transactionId %></span></div>
    <div class="info-row"><span>Amount</span><span>৳<%= amount.toFixed(2) %></span></div>
    <p style="margin-top:16px;">You can retry the payment from your orders page, or contact support if the issue persists.</p>
    <div class="cta"><a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/my-orders">Retry Payment</a></div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Mission Bazar</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
